channel.description:

client.java:1: class, interface, or enum expected import java.io.*;(server name is here) ^ 1 error Finished! Press any key to continue . . .

item.title: Changing server info?

item.description:

I would like to note:
If it gives you anything like that

client.java:1: class, interface, or enum expected
import java.io.*;(server name is here)
                 ^
1 error
Finished!
Press any key to continue . . .

then that is an error.

if it gives steam deprecated blah blah blah , than your compile was successful.
